<div class="sl-modes">
  <div class="sl-modes__inner">

    <div class="sl-modes__media">
      <img src="{{ 'info-3modes.webp' | asset_url }}" alt="SilkLift 3 Advanced Modes — RF, UP, LF" loading="lazy" class="sl-modes__img" width="731" height="1200">
    </div>

    <div class="sl-modes__content">
      <p class="sl-modes__eyebrow">Why Everything Else Has Failed You</p>
      <h2 class="sl-modes__heading">3 Clinically-Backed<br><em>Modes. One Fix.</em></h2>
      <p class="sl-modes__intro">Serums sit on your skin's surface — they can't go deeper than 0.1mm. Botox costs $700 a session, carries real risks of drooping and nerve damage, and wears off in 90 days. Sun exposure has been silently destroying your collagen for years. SilkLift penetrates where nothing else can reach — and actually rebuilds.</p>

      <div class="sl-modes__list">

        <div class="sl-mode-item">
          <div class="sl-mode-item__icon">RF</div>
          <div class="sl-mode-item__text">
            <p class="sl-mode-item__name">Radiofrequency — Deep Collagen Rebuild</p>
            <p class="sl-mode-item__desc">RF energy heats the dermis to 40–43°C — the exact temperature that triggers your body to produce new collagen. Clinical studies show up to 37% increase in collagen density after 4 weeks. This is the same technology used in $400 clinic sessions. No needles. No downtime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sl-mode-item">
          <div class="sl-mode-item__icon">UP</div>
          <div class="sl-mode-item__text">
            <p class="sl-mode-item__name">Microcurrent — The Natural Face Lift</p>
            <p class="sl-mode-item__desc">Micro-electrical pulses mirror your body's own bio-electric signals, retraining facial muscles that have weakened and drooped over time. Immediate visible lift after one session. Cumulative sculpting after 4 weeks. Used by celebrities and their aestheticians worldwide — now $99.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sl-mode-item">
          <div class="sl-mode-item__icon" style="background:#8B0000;color:#ffcdd2">RL</div>
          <div class="sl-mode-item__text">
            <p class="sl-mode-item__name">Red Light Therapy — Cellular Sun Damage Repair</p>
            <p class="sl-mode-item__desc">630–850nm red and near-infrared wavelengths penetrate 5–10mm beneath the skin surface — deep enough to reach damaged cells. Originally developed by NASA for wound healing. Clinically proven to reverse UV-induced collagen breakdown, reduce hyperpigmentation, calm inflammation, and accelerate cellular repair. The most powerful anti-aging tool hiding in plain sight.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <a href="/products/silklift-rf-pro" class="sl-btn sl-btn--gold sl-btn--big">Stop Aging. Start Repairing — $99 →</a>
      <p class="sl-modes__note">✓ Free shipping &nbsp;·&nbsp; ✓ 30-Day Guarantee &nbsp;·&nbsp; ✓ No needles. No clinic visits.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
.sl-modes {
  background: #FAF8F5;
  padding: 80px 40px;
}

.sl-modes__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 45% 55%;
  gap: 60px;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  align-items: center;
}

.sl-modes__media {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.sl-modes__img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.sl-modes__eyebrow {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #C9956A;
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}

.sl-modes__heading {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.0;
  color: #2C2C2C;
  margin: 0 0 20px;
}

.sl-modes__heading em { font-style: italic; }

.sl-modes__intro {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: #5A5350;
  margin: 0 0 36px;
}

.sl-modes__list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}

.sl-mode-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 18px;
}

.sl-mode-item__icon {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  background: #2C2C2C;
  color: #C9956A;
  padding: 8px 10px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  min-width: 42px;
  text-align: center;
}

.sl-mode-item__name {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #2C2C2C;
  margin: 0 0 4px;
}

.sl-mode-item__desc {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: #8A7F78;
  margin: 0;
}

.sl-modes__note {
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  color: #8A7F78;
  margin: 12px 0 0;
}

.sl-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 18px 32px;
  transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
}
.sl-btn--big { font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 20px 40px; }
.sl-btn:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px); }
.sl-btn--gold { background: #C9956A; color: #FAF8F5; border: 2px solid #C9956A; }

@media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
  .sl-modes { padding: 60px 20px; }
  .sl-modes__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
  .sl-modes__media { max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .sl-btn { width: 100%; }
}
{% endstylesheet %}

